細菌感染, 如果遲多少少睇就保唔返隻腳掌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7171060d037b70f680b10adf56901a2a8798aadd","tid":1006402,"uid":985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T01:23:56.000Z","msg":"睇過物理治療同跌打推拿，兩個都係令我肌肉relaxed翻。<br />\n物理治療就電，吸同熱敷加拉腰，收600，無教動作。<br />\n都有鬆d，但效果無跌打好，仲係有小小唔舒服加第二日又緊翻小小。<br />\n跌打就針灸，曬燈，推拿，收300<br />\n個人感覺，跌打做完一次，明顯鬆d同無痛，不過一排又會再痛，佢叫我要成日去。<br />\n利申:輕微椎間盤突出，照過mri l4/l5"},{"pid":"2c213fecf9c7fdc9820a78a32a69eb8fcac60874","tid":1006402,"uid":66686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"039489fd97a4ef380622d957242fa54036e8059c","tid":1006402,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T01:18:14.000Z","msg":"如果個趺打師傅廢D 好易整傷埋你其他位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算好手勢有經驗既都未必好<br />\n以前老細打拳整親隻腳掌 去左睇趺打, 卒完又full完藥成個星期都未好<br />\n之後去醫院check先知係細菌感染, 如果遲多少少睇就保唔返隻腳掌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T04:49:03.000Z","msg":"所以話中醫真係斷鳩估<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0056b7d0b18ac18facc4e337c613ca16e6776df","tid":1006402,"uid":34300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c213fecf9c7fdc9820a78a32a69eb8fcac60874","tid":1006402,"uid":66686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"039489fd97a4ef380622d957242fa54036e8059c","tid":1006402,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T01:18:14.000Z","msg":"如果個趺打師傅廢D 好易整傷埋你其他位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算好手勢有經驗既都未必好<br />\n以前老細打拳整親隻腳掌 去左睇趺打, 卒完又full完藥成個星期都未好<br />\n之後去醫院check先知係細菌感染, 如果遲多少少睇就保唔返隻腳掌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif